# This query retrieves all columns from the `order_mt4` table for orders that are associated with a specific client ID (100600). It performs a join with the `account_opt` table to match orders based on their source and login information. The results are ordered by the close time of the orders in ascending order, meaning the earliest closed orders will appear first. The `LIMIT 10` clause restricts the output to the top 10 records, providing a snapshot of the earliest closed orders for that client.
